some hints for sphinx:

yum install python-sphinx

http://www.sphinx-doc.org/en/stable/index.html
http://www.sphinx-doc.org/en/stable/tutorial.html
http://www.sphinx-doc.org/en/stable/markup/inline.html#ref-role

may "ifconfig module" is interessting for selecting, which
parts we add.

sphinx-quickstart

set PYTHONPATH for creating tbotlib function documentation
export PYTHONPATH=/home/hs/data/Entwicklung/tbot/src/common:/home/hs/data/Entwicklung/tbot/src/common/event:/home/hs/data/Entwicklung/tbot/src/lab_api

create HTML:
make html;firefox build/html/main.html

create pdf:
https://www.quora.com/How-to-create-a-PDF-out-of-Sphinx-documentation-tool
sphinx-build -b pdf source build/pdf;okular build/pdf/tbot_doc.pdf
